110
00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:16.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我知道 她是和栗同学</c.simplifiedchinese>

111
00:08:16.662 --> 00:08:18.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>和栗同学？</c.simplifiedchinese>

112
00:08:18.247 --> 00:08:20.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>她每个月都会来几次</c.simplifiedchinese>

113
00:08:20.666 --> 00:08:22.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我们聊过之后就变熟了</c.simplifiedchinese>

114
00:08:22.710 --> 00:08:24.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>是常客啊</c.simplifiedchinese>

115
00:08:24.128 --> 00:08:26.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>话说 你问这个做什么？</c.simplifiedchinese>

116
00:08:26.923 --> 00:08:27.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>（紧盯）</c.simplifiedchinese>

117
00:08:27.924 --> 00:08:28.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>说啊</c.simplifiedchinese>

118
00:08:30.593 --> 00:08:33.596 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>那个女生看到我就逃跑了</c.simplifiedchinese>

119
00:08:34.138 --> 00:08:37.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>可能被我害得以后都不来了 抱歉</c.simplifiedchinese>

120
00:08:37.600 --> 00:08:40.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这怎么会是你的错？</c.simplifiedchinese>

121
00:08:40.394 --> 00:08:42.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>和栗同学不是那样的人</c.simplifiedchinese>

122
00:08:42.813 --> 00:08:45.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>而且你总是爱把什么事都归咎于自己</c.simplifiedchinese>

123
00:08:45.441 --> 00:08:46.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这是你的坏习惯喔</c.simplifiedchinese>

124
00:08:49.695 --> 00:08:52.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不过万一她真的不来
我就要拿蛋糕来一决胜负了</c.simplifiedchinese>

125
00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:53.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>（熊熊燃烧）</c.simplifiedchinese>

126
00:08:53.658 --> 00:08:56.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我要再次让她成为我甜点的俘虏</c.simplifiedchinese>

127
00:09:01.624 --> 00:09:03.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>走咯</c.simplifiedchinese>

128
00:09:03.209 --> 00:09:05.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>肚子饿了</c.simplifiedchinese>

129
00:09:07.463 --> 00:09:11.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>如果让那个女生
留下心理创伤怎么办？</c.simplifiedchinese>

130
00:09:11.551 --> 00:09:14.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>去附近的初中找人道歉似乎也不太好</c.simplifiedchinese>

131
00:09:15.429 --> 00:09:18.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>应该说那样绝对会被当作可疑人士</c.simplifiedchinese>

132
00:09:18.182 --> 00:09:19.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你怎么了？</c.simplifiedchinese>

133
00:09:20.977 --> 00:09:22.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>在烦恼什么？</c.simplifiedchinese>

134
00:09:23.020 --> 00:09:24.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>轮到我们出场了吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

135
00:09:24.230 --> 00:09:26.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不用 我没事</c.simplifiedchinese>

136
00:09:28.276 --> 00:09:30.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我去买午餐 你们先吃吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

137
00:09:30.945 --> 00:09:32.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>好</c.simplifiedchinese>

138
00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:40.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>总觉得跟凛太郎之间</c.simplifiedchinese>

139
00:09:41.414 --> 00:09:43.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>有种隔着一道墙的感觉</c.simplifiedchinese>

140
00:09:52.550 --> 00:09:53.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>怎么了？</c.simplifiedchinese>

141
00:09:54.427 --> 00:09:55.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>凛太郎</c.simplifiedchinese>

142
00:09:57.263 --> 00:09:58.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>和栗同学来了</c.simplifiedchinese>

143
00:09:58.931 --> 00:10:00.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>她说有事找你</c.simplifiedchinese>

144
00:10:12.236 --> 00:10:13.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>她真的来了</c.simplifiedchinese>

145
00:10:14.071 --> 00:10:15.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你好</c.simplifiedchinese>

146
00:10:18.242 --> 00:10:20.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>那个…</c.simplifiedchinese>

147
00:10:21.037 --> 00:10:22.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>昨天…</c.simplifiedchinese>

148
00:10:24.290 --> 00:10:26.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我请客吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

149
00:10:29.420 --> 00:10:30.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>什么？</c.simplifiedchinese>

150
00:10:32.715 --> 00:10:36.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>《薰香花朵凛然绽放》</c.simplifiedchinese>

151
00:10:44.435 --> 00:10:48.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不对 这是怎样？在自己家
被比自己小的女生请吃自家的蛋糕？</c.simplifiedchinese>

152
00:10:48.898 --> 00:10:49.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>那个…</c.simplifiedchinese>

153
00:10:50.441 --> 00:10:54.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>抱歉昨天突然就跑走了</c.simplifiedchinese>

154
00:10:56.113 --> 00:10:59.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这个蛋糕是给你的赔礼 请享用吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

155
00:10:59.158 --> 00:11:00.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不了</c.simplifiedchinese>

156
00:11:01.827 --> 00:11:02.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这怎么行？</c.simplifiedchinese>

157
00:11:09.251 --> 00:11:10.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>请用</c.simplifiedchinese>

158
00:11:10.336 --> 00:11:12.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>咦？不行 这是给你的</c.simplifiedchinese>

159
00:11:13.547 --> 00:11:14.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>没关系</c.simplifiedchinese>

160
00:11:15.299 --> 00:11:17.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这个很好吃喔 请吃吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

161
00:11:19.136 --> 00:11:20.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>可是…</c.simplifiedchinese>

162
00:11:28.145 --> 00:11:30.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不好意思 我开动了</c.simplifiedchinese>

163
00:11:30.314 --> 00:11:31.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>好的</c.simplifiedchinese>

164
00:11:32.149 --> 00:11:34.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不只是蛋糕</c.simplifiedchinese>

165
00:11:34.944 --> 00:11:37.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这个女生很喜欢吃东西呢</c.simplifiedchinese>

166
00:11:41.450 --> 00:11:42.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>欢迎光临</c.simplifiedchinese>

167
00:11:43.828 --> 00:11:45.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你应该吃了一惊吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

168
00:11:46.539 --> 00:11:48.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>-什么？
-就是昨天那时候</c.simplifiedchinese>

169
00:11:49.041 --> 00:11:52.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你应该没看过食量那么大的人吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

170
00:11:57.675 --> 00:11:58.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>确实</c.simplifiedchinese>

171
00:11:59.760 --> 00:12:00.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>对吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

172
00:12:01.470 --> 00:12:05.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>因为刚好店里没有别的客人
就没忍到回家再吃</c.simplifiedchinese>

173
00:12:09.228 --> 00:12:12.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>可以请问你叫什么名字吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

174
00:12:12.731 --> 00:12:15.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我是和栗薰子</c.simplifiedchinese>

175
00:12:16.193 --> 00:12:18.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我叫紬凛太郎</c.simplifiedchinese>

176
00:12:20.197 --> 00:12:22.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这样啊 凛太郎同学</c.simplifiedchinese>

177
00:12:24.201 --> 00:12:25.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>是凛太郎同学啊</c.simplifiedchinese>

178
00:12:26.704 --> 00:12:30.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>她为什么会想知道我的事呢？</c.simplifiedchinese>

179
00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:32.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>总算知道了</c.simplifiedchinese>

180
00:12:34.170 --> 00:12:35.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>总算？</c.simplifiedchinese>

181
00:12:36.839 --> 00:12:40.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>那个…不是的</c.simplifiedchinese>

182
00:12:40.676 --> 00:12:41.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不要误会</c.simplifiedchinese>

183
00:12:41.802 --> 00:12:46.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>其实我之前就有看过凛太郎同学</c.simplifiedchinese>

184
00:12:47.099 --> 00:12:49.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你偶尔会来这边帮忙对吧？</c.simplifiedchinese>

185
00:12:49.977 --> 00:12:51.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>是啊</c.simplifiedchinese>

186
00:12:52.771 --> 00:12:55.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>所以昨天不是初次见面啊</c.simplifiedchinese>

187
00:12:55.941 --> 00:12:57.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我都没发现</c.simplifiedchinese>

188
00:12:58.611 --> 00:12:59.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>咦？</c.simplifiedchinese>

189
00:12:59.528 --> 00:13:02.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>所以不是因为我太可怕
把你吓跑的吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

190
00:13:02.823 --> 00:13:04.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>什么？不是喔</c.simplifiedchinese>

191
00:13:04.867 --> 00:13:06.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我之前就看过你好几次了</c.simplifiedchinese>

192
00:13:06.327 --> 00:13:07.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>（凛太郎 太吵了）</c.simplifiedchinese>

193
00:13:07.244 --> 00:13:08.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>那为什么要逃走…</c.simplifiedchinese>

194
00:13:08.162 --> 00:13:08.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>（真有精神）</c.simplifiedchinese>

195
00:13:09.079 --> 00:13:10.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>那个…</c.simplifiedchinese>

196
00:13:11.081 --> 00:13:12.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>就是…</c.simplifiedchinese>

197
00:13:13.417 --> 00:13:17.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我还是第一次那样被男性盯着看</c.simplifiedchinese>

198
00:13:18.506 --> 00:13:21.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>心跳得太快 所以…</c.simplifiedchinese>

199
00:13:24.553 --> 00:13:26.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>什么？心跳太快？</c.simplifiedchinese>

200
00:13:26.722 --> 00:13:28.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>对我吗？为什么？</c.simplifiedchinese>

201
00:13:29.183 --> 00:13:33.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>一般被我这种人盯着看只会害怕吧？</c.simplifiedchinese>

202
00:13:33.687 --> 00:13:35.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>至今为止我遇到的
几乎都是这样的情况</c.simplifiedchinese>

203
00:13:41.195 --> 00:13:43.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>搞不懂啦</c.simplifiedchinese>

204
00:13:44.365 --> 00:13:46.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>天色已经很晚了</c.simplifiedchinese>

205
00:13:47.034 --> 00:13:49.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我送你到车站吧 不然很危险的</c.simplifiedchinese>

206
00:13:49.453 --> 00:13:50.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>咦？</c.simplifiedchinese>

207
00:13:50.829 --> 00:13:52.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>真的呢</c.simplifiedchinese>

208
00:13:52.623 --> 00:13:56.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>那可以先让我买个蛋糕吗？
我会尽快的</c.simplifiedchinese>

209
00:13:56.085 --> 00:13:58.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>咦？好啊</c.simplifiedchinese>

210
00:14:02.091 --> 00:14:04.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>真的不用送你吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

211
00:14:05.427 --> 00:14:08.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>没问题的 而且这里离车站本来就近</c.simplifiedchinese>

212
00:14:09.348 --> 00:14:10.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>那我先告辞了</c.simplifiedchinese>

213
00:14:17.022 --> 00:14:18.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>对了</c.simplifiedchinese>

214
00:14:20.651 --> 00:14:24.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你刚刚问说 我是不是被你吓跑的</c.simplifiedchinese>

215
00:14:25.072 --> 00:14:29.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我一次都没有觉得凛太郎同学可怕喔</c.simplifiedchinese>

216
00:14:31.787 --> 00:14:33.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>相信我</c.simplifiedchinese>

217
00:14:36.041 --> 00:14:37.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>谢谢招待</c.simplifiedchinese>

218
00:14:45.968 --> 00:14:47.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>凛太郎 别吵</c.simplifiedchinese>

219
00:14:55.895 --> 00:14:57.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我真的搞不懂</c.simplifiedchinese>

220
00:14:58.814 --> 00:15:01.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>凛太郎很可怕吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

221
00:15:02.318 --> 00:15:04.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我之前还被他瞪了</c.simplifiedchinese>

222
00:15:04.695 --> 00:15:07.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>听说凛太郎家里是开蛋糕店的？</c.simplifiedchinese>

223
00:15:07.615 --> 00:15:10.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>他吗？超不适合的</c.simplifiedchinese>

224
00:15:12.202 --> 00:15:13.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>从小时候开始</c.simplifiedchinese>

225
00:15:14.496 --> 00:15:17.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我听过的都只有别人的否定</c.simplifiedchinese>

226
00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:21.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>心跳得太快 所以…</c.simplifiedchinese>

227
00:15:22.129 --> 00:15:26.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我一次都没有觉得凛太郎同学可怕喔</c.simplifiedchinese>

228
00:15:31.847 --> 00:15:33.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>凛太郎</c.simplifiedchinese>

229
00:15:34.266 --> 00:15:36.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>-你做什么啊？
-这个</c.simplifiedchinese>

230
00:15:36.352 --> 00:15:39.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这是和栗同学的蛋糕吧？</c.simplifiedchinese>

231
00:15:40.064 --> 00:15:43.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>靠近一看 你真的好小只喔</c.simplifiedchinese>

232
00:15:43.609 --> 00:15:45.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>真可爱</c.simplifiedchinese>

233
00:15:45.110 --> 00:15:47.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>请放开我</c.simplifiedchinese>

234
00:15:47.404 --> 00:15:52.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>别这么说嘛 跟我们一起去玩吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

235
00:15:57.998 --> 00:16:02.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我正打算关店 走出去时
就看到这个掉在路边</c.simplifiedchinese>

236
00:16:03.045 --> 00:16:05.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>和栗同学有安全到家吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

237
00:16:08.342 --> 00:16:09.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>在哪里？</c.simplifiedchinese>

238
00:16:09.259 --> 00:16:12.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>话说你刚刚为什么跟凛太郎在一起？</c.simplifiedchinese>

239
00:16:12.888 --> 00:16:14.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你是他女友吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

240
00:16:14.598 --> 00:16:15.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不是</c.simplifiedchinese>

241
00:16:15.516 --> 00:16:17.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>也是</c.simplifiedchinese>

242
00:16:17.267 --> 00:16:19.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>毕竟你跟他是完全相反的类型</c.simplifiedchinese>

243
00:16:19.895 --> 00:16:21.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>他们是昨天的…</c.simplifiedchinese>

244
00:16:21.981 --> 00:16:23.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>为什么会在这里？</c.simplifiedchinese>

245
00:16:23.315 --> 00:16:25.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>那家伙是出了名的恐怖喔</c.simplifiedchinese>

246
00:16:25.859 --> 00:16:28.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你知道吗？听说他是不良少年呢</c.simplifiedchinese>

247
00:16:28.362 --> 00:16:29.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不良少年？</c.simplifiedchinese>

248
00:16:30.990 --> 00:16:33.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>是啊 那家伙初中时好像也很夸张</c.simplifiedchinese>

249
00:16:34.785 --> 00:16:37.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我是从认识他的人那里听说的</c.simplifiedchinese>

250
00:16:37.413 --> 00:16:40.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>然后现在读了所放牛学校
还跟着一群跟班</c.simplifiedchinese>

251
00:16:41.041 --> 00:16:43.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>跟他厮混没什么好处的</c.simplifiedchinese>

252
00:16:44.211 --> 00:16:45.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>原来如此</c.simplifiedchinese>

253
00:16:46.046 --> 00:16:50.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>就是因为他们在乱造谣
才会一直有怪人找上门来</c.simplifiedchinese>

254
00:16:51.635 --> 00:16:55.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不过我上的确实是放牛学校
这也没办法</c.simplifiedchinese>

255
00:16:57.057 --> 00:16:58.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>是这样啊</c.simplifiedchinese>

256
00:16:59.518 --> 00:17:00.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>真可怕呢</c.simplifiedchinese>

257
00:17:00.853 --> 00:17:04.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>对吧？跟那种人在一起很危险的</c.simplifiedchinese>

258
00:17:04.189 --> 00:17:06.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>所以你就和我们…</c.simplifiedchinese>

259
00:17:06.567 --> 00:17:10.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>为什么你们能光凭谣言
就断定一个人的为人呢？</c.simplifiedchinese>

260
00:17:13.323 --> 00:17:14.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>什么？</c.simplifiedchinese>

261
00:17:14.658 --> 00:17:17.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你们跟凛太郎同学说过话吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

262
00:17:17.536 --> 00:17:19.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>要不要试着和他聊一次？</c.simplifiedchinese>

263
00:17:19.538 --> 00:17:21.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不要 有什么好聊的？</c.simplifiedchinese>

264
00:17:21.707 --> 00:17:24.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这样你一定就会知道
他是个很好的人了</c.simplifiedchinese>

265
00:17:25.044 --> 00:17:28.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>他好不好跟我无关</c.simplifiedchinese>

266
00:17:30.883 --> 00:17:34.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>如果你不愿意 那也没关系</c.simplifiedchinese>

267
00:17:34.803 --> 00:17:40.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>既然你不愿意去了解他
那至少可以请你不要擅自诋毁他吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

268
00:17:42.561 --> 00:17:43.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这让我很不愉快</c.simplifiedchinese>

269
00:17:46.815 --> 00:17:48.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>真是的</c.simplifiedchinese>

270
00:17:49.610 --> 00:17:53.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>看你跟他亲近
想说要是能利用你来整他就好了</c.simplifiedchinese>

271
00:17:55.657 --> 00:17:57.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>但我改变心意了</c.simplifiedchinese>

272
00:18:04.416 --> 00:18:05.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你…</c.simplifiedchinese>

273
00:18:05.459 --> 00:18:07.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>为什么会在这里？</c.simplifiedchinese>

274
00:18:10.172 --> 00:18:13.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你说想整我？</c.simplifiedchinese>

275
00:18:16.053 --> 00:18:17.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这样满意了吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

276
00:18:19.890 --> 00:18:21.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>非常抱歉</c.simplifiedchinese>

277
00:18:25.813 --> 00:18:27.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>凛…太郎同学</c.simplifiedchinese>

278
00:18:28.357 --> 00:18:29.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你流血了</c.simplifiedchinese>

279
00:18:31.902 --> 00:18:33.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>对不起</c.simplifiedchinese>

280
00:18:34.196 --> 00:18:36.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这不是你的错</c.simplifiedchinese>

281
00:18:36.323 --> 00:18:40.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>而且与其说被打
其实是因为反作用力撞到墙了</c.simplifiedchinese>

282
00:18:40.911 --> 00:18:43.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>不管哪种都不行</c.simplifiedchinese>

283
00:18:44.039 --> 00:18:44.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>抱歉</c.simplifiedchinese>

284
00:18:45.499 --> 00:18:48.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>要是知道你会这么困扰
我就会直接挡下那一拳了</c.simplifiedchinese>

285
00:18:48.460 --> 00:18:50.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你是故意被打到的吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

286
00:18:50.504 --> 00:18:51.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>为什么呢？</c.simplifiedchinese>

287
00:18:52.923 --> 00:18:55.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>算是惩罚吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

288
00:18:56.009 --> 00:18:56.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>咦？</c.simplifiedchinese>

289
00:18:58.095 --> 00:19:00.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你明明说了要我相信你的 我却…</c.simplifiedchinese>

290
00:19:01.431 --> 00:19:04.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>对不起 害你被卷入这种事情</c.simplifiedchinese>

291
00:19:04.685 --> 00:19:07.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>别这么说 请把头抬起来吧</c.simplifiedchinese>

292
00:19:07.521 --> 00:19:09.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这不是凛太郎同学的错</c.simplifiedchinese>

293
00:19:11.984 --> 00:19:13.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>就是我的错</c.simplifiedchinese>

294
00:19:14.153 --> 00:19:18.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>既然你不愿意去了解他
那至少可以请你不要擅自诋毁他吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

295
00:19:19.408 --> 00:19:23.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>居然让这么温柔的人
遭遇了这种恐怖的经历</c.simplifiedchinese>

296
00:19:23.787 --> 00:19:24.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>都是我的错</c.simplifiedchinese>

297
00:19:26.707 --> 00:19:28.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>对不起</c.simplifiedchinese>

298
00:19:31.670 --> 00:19:34.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>真的好不可思议</c.simplifiedchinese>

299
00:19:34.882 --> 00:19:38.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我完全不知道你有哪里可怕</c.simplifiedchinese>

300
00:19:40.137 --> 00:19:42.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你明明这么地温柔</c.simplifiedchinese>

301
00:19:45.184 --> 00:19:47.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>对了 我还没对你说</c.simplifiedchinese>

302
00:19:49.938 --> 00:19:52.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>谢谢你救了我</c.simplifiedchinese>

303
00:19:55.235 --> 00:19:56.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>可恶</c.simplifiedchinese>

304
00:19:58.655 --> 00:20:02.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>这副外表已经让我习惯了被人否定</c.simplifiedchinese>

305
00:20:02.367 --> 00:20:04.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>对别人的评价没有一丝期待</c.simplifiedchinese>

306
00:20:06.538 --> 00:20:08.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>明明已经放弃了</c.simplifiedchinese>

307
00:20:09.041 --> 00:20:12.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>现在却萌生出了渴望</c.simplifiedchinese>

308
00:20:18.050 --> 00:20:19.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>（红之丘站 北出口）</c.simplifiedchinese>

309
00:20:19.092 --> 00:20:21.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>谢谢你特地送我过来</c.simplifiedchinese>

310
00:20:21.553 --> 00:20:24.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>你的伤没事吧？</c.simplifiedchinese>

311
00:20:24.223 --> 00:20:26.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>没事 这种伤很快就好了</c.simplifiedchinese>

312
00:20:26.808 --> 00:20:29.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>回家路上小心</c.simplifiedchinese>

313
00:20:29.728 --> 00:20:31.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>是 我会小心的</c.simplifiedchinese>

314
00:20:32.898 --> 00:20:34.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>那我走了</c.simplifiedchinese>

315
00:20:43.867 --> 00:20:45.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>凛太郎同学</c.simplifiedchinese>

316
00:20:46.620 --> 00:20:47.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>什么？</c.simplifiedchinese>

317
00:20:47.663 --> 00:20:50.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>我会再去店里吃东西的</c.simplifiedchinese>

318
00:20:52.251 --> 00:20:53.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>所以</c.simplifiedchinese>

319
00:20:55.170 --> 00:20:58.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>下次一起吃吧 一起吃蛋糕</c.simplifiedchinese>

320
00:21:03.053 --> 00:21:04.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>好的</c.simplifiedchinese>

321
00:21:11.687 --> 00:21:12.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>是</c.simplifiedchinese>

322
00:21:14.856 --> 00:21:16.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>对 我没事</c.simplifiedchinese>

323
00:21:17.276 --> 00:21:18.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>已经在回去路上了</c.simplifiedchinese>

324
00:21:43.260 --> 00:21:45.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>太早来了</c.simplifiedchinese>

325
00:21:45.762 --> 00:21:48.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>好困 昨天完全睡不着</c.simplifiedchinese>

326
00:21:51.310 --> 00:21:52.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>谢谢你</c.simplifiedchinese>

327
00:21:56.898 --> 00:22:00.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>和栗同学下次什么时候会来店里呢？</c.simplifiedchinese>

328
00:22:05.157 --> 00:22:06.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>什么？</c.simplifiedchinese>

329
00:22:07.159 --> 00:22:08.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>真稀奇</c.simplifiedchinese>

330
00:22:09.244 --> 00:22:10.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>要拉开窗帘吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

331
00:22:22.257 --> 00:22:25.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>为什么？为什么和栗同学会在那里？</c.simplifiedchinese>

332
00:22:25.093 --> 00:22:27.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>话说 她不是比我小吗？</c.simplifiedchinese>

333
00:22:31.475 --> 00:22:32.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>和栗同学</c.simplifiedchinese>

334
00:22:33.977 --> 00:22:35.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>是桔梗的学生？</c.simplifiedchinese>

335
00:22:37.022 --> 00:22:39.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.simplifiedchinese>第1集：凛太郎与薰子</c.simplifiedchinese>

336
00:22:39.316 --> 00:22:40.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
